typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		policyID as string,
		statecode as string,
		county as string,
		eq_site_limit as double,
		hu_site_limit as double,
		fl_site_limit as double,
		fr_site_limit as double,
		tiv_2011 as double,
		tiv_2012 as double,
		eq_site_deductible as double,
		hu_site_deductible as double,
		fl_site_deductible as double,
		fr_site_deductible as double,
		point_latitude as double,
		point_longitude as double,
		line as string,
		construction as string,
		point_granularity as integer,
		GeoLocation as binary
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: false,
	validateSchema: false,
	limit: 100,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_COMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source1
source1 aggregate() ~> Aggregate1
